metadata.name: Artaxia #1
metadata.description: Artaxia is a collection of 1143 unique pieces created by three talented artists. Our project is designed for art and sci-fi enthusiasts and features a stunning comic series that immerses you in an exciting world of adventure and intrigue. Our community of collectors and enthusiasts has grown significantly following the success of our previous collection, 'Dirty Taco NFT'. Artaxia is the first in a series of three sister projects, with two already finished and available for holders, and the third one coming soon. Artaxia is the vision of a successful restaurant owner who has brought his passion for creativity and love of sci-fi to this unique project. Join us on this journey and own a piece of Artaxia's captivating world. Thank you for your support!
